; Part 1: Caesar Cipher (Manual) 
; The Caesar cipher shifts each letter by a fixed number. Example: with shift 3, HELLO -> KHOOR 
; 
; Exercise 1.1: Encrypt (Shift Right 5) 
; Plaintext         Your Answer 
; MEET ME AT NOON = RJJY RJ EY SPPS
; SECURITY        = XJHZWNYD
; 
; Exercise 1.2: Decrypt (Shift Left 7) 
; Ciphertext        Your Answer 
; OLSSV           = HELLO
;
; -----------------------------------------------
; Reference Table:
; a,0,     j,9,   s,18             
; b,1,     k,10,   t,19
; c,2,     l,11,   u,20
; d,3,     m,12,   v,21
; e,4,     n,13,   w,22
; f,5,     o,14,   x,23
; g,6,     p,15,   y,24
; h,7,     q,16,   z,25
; i,8,     r,17,
